Ranger Help for: check
======================

SYNTAX:      check <terrain>
USAGE:       Anywhere.

SUMMARY:
Shows all Ranger skills that can be used in the specified terrain,
along with their slot costs. Useful for planning which skills to
learn based on where you like to adventure.

Example: check forest
         check mountain
         check underground

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: terrains, survey, skills
